 <div style="max-width:180mm;">
  <img alt="ss-span-cl.png" class="side" src="Images/structures/rc/spans/ss-span-cl.png" style="height:170pt;"/>
  <h4>Dimensions</h4>
  <p>
   Clear spans (
   <i>l</i>
   <sub>x</sub>
