   </p>
   <p class="ref">[EN 1992-1-1, §. 9.2.1.1 (1)]</p>
   <p>Minimum reinforcement ratio</p>
   <p>
    <span class="eq">
     <var>ρ</var>
     <sub>min</sub>
     =
     <b>max</b>
     <span class="b1">(</span>
     <span class="dvc">
      0.26 ·
      <var>f</var>
      <sub>ctm</sub>
      <span class="dvl">
      </span>
      <var>f</var>
      <sub>yk</sub>
     </span>
     ; 0.0013
     <span class="b1">)</span>
     =
     <b>max</b>
     <span class="b1">(</span>
